      <a href="#">[ref-xschema-2]</a>.]</p> 
    </dd> 
   
    
    <dt class="label">model item</dt> 
    <dd> 
      <p>[<a title="model item" name="def-model-item">Definition</a>: An abstract unit of data-collection
